    "original_goal": "Migrate the TC387 GTM TOM 3-phase inverter PWM to TC4D7 eGTM ATOM using the unified IfxEgtm_Pwm driver.",
    "functional_behavior": "Generate 3-phase, 20 kHz center-aligned complementary PWM with 1 µs rising/falling deadtime via DTM, per-phase independent duty updates with synchronous apply on period event, and one period interrupt on CPU0 (priority 20).",
    "technical_approach": "Use the unified IfxEgtm_Pwm on TC4D7 eGTM Cluster 1, ATOM1 CH0/1/2; enable EGTM CMU Clk1 at 100 MHz; map pins using IfxEgtm_PinMap to KIT_A3G_TC4D7_LITE macros; configure center-aligned counting and DTM deadtime through IfxEgtm_Pwm; perform duty updates using non-immediate APIs for synchronous on-period apply; install a single period ISR on CPU0."
  },
